3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses a probabilistic model to represent robot skills, which is a common technique in machine learning. 
4. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper mentions using simulated assembly tasks, which may involve computer vision techniques for object recognition and tracking. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the use of a real robot experiment with a UR5, which involves control and system integration.
